OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLate
OL,6,Fsunshine for many to end Tuesday. Low
OL,7,Fcloud in the North Sea expanding and
OL,8,Fspreading inland overnight, though
OL,9,Fclear spells holding on in the west.
OL,10,FBreezy in the south but feeling warm
OL,11,Fhere. A fresher night in the north.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FLow cloud retreating to
OL,14,Feastern coasts, leaving another fine
OL,15,Fand dry day with prolonged sunny
OL,16,Fperiods. Chance of an odd thundery
OL,17,Fshower in the southwest. Very warm or
OL,18,Fhot.
